<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Welcome to AudioLounge</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <img src="<%= imageUrl %>" alt="AudioLounge Banner" width="600" height="200" />
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <h1>Welcome to AudioLounge! 🎉</h1>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <p>Dear <%= name %> 👋,</p>
          <p>
            Thank you for joining AudioLounge, the ultimate platform for hosting and participating in captivating audio
            events on a wide range of topics. We are thrilled to have you as part of our community! 🎧🌟
          </p>
          <p>
            At AudioLounge, we believe in the power of conversations and the impact they can have on personal growth and
            collective knowledge. Our mission is to create a vibrant space where individuals from all walks of life can
            connect, converse, and share their thoughts in real-time, fostering meaningful discussions and
            knowledge-sharing. 🗣️💡
          </p>
          <p>
            With AudioLounge, you can explore a diverse range of audio events, including panel discussions, interviews,
            workshops, and more. Engage with experts, thought leaders, and fellow enthusiasts to expand your horizons,
            gain insights, and build valuable connections. 🌍🔊
          </p>
          <p>
            We encourage you to explore our platform, discover events that align with your interests, and actively
            participate in the discussions. Your unique perspectives and contributions will enrich the conversations and
            create a dynamic environment for everyone involved. 🌈💬
          </p>
          <p>
            If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always here to help. Feel free to reach
            out to us at support@audiolounge.com. 📧🤝
          </p>
          <p>Once again, welcome to AudioLounge! We're excited to embark on this audio journey with you. 🎙️✨</p>
          <p>
            Best regards,<br />
            The AudioLounge Team 🎧🌟
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
